<span>Serving New Haven County</span>
</div>
<p class="lead">Expert vocational evaluation services for Naugatuck attorneys and insurance professionals. Comprehensive earning capacity assessments, employability evaluations, and labor market analysis. Serving Naugatuck attorneys with expert vocational services through virtual consultations and in-person meetings.</p>
